These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Game: domino, backgammon, snooker, billiard
Pet: goat, lizard, ferret, rabbit
1. Game:snooker is between Pet:ferret and Pet:lizard##2
2. Game:billiard is on the left or right of Pet:ferret##3
3. Pet:ferret is not to the left of Pet:ferret##8
4. Pet:lizard != Game:snooker##6
5. Game:snooker is somewhere to the right of Game:domino##5
6. Game:domino is on the right of Pet:goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | billiard  | domino | snooker | backgammon  |
| Pet   | goat | ferret   | rabbit  | lizard |

