.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
City: colone, boston, prague, london
Hobby: traveling, writing, hiking, gardening
1. Hobby:gardening is not to the left of Hobby:gardening##8
2. City:colone is somewhere to the right of City:london##5
3. City:colone == Hobby:writing##1
4. City:london is between City:colone and City:boston##2
5. City:boston is somewhere between City:prague and Hobby:traveling##7
6. Hobby:hiking is somewhere to the left of City:boston##5
7. Hobby:traveling is not to the left of Hobby:traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| City   | prague | boston          | london | colone     |
| Hobby    | hiking      | gardening | traveling | writing |

