2. Sport:tennis is on the far left##1
3. Cigar:bongani is on the right of Cigar:vegafina##1
4. Cigar:bongani is in an even position##4
5. Cigar:blend is on the far left or far right##3
6. Cigar:vegafina is somewhere to the left of Sport:lacrosse##5
7. Cigar:blend == Sport:snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | vegafina | bongani | bolivar     | blend |
| Sport   | tennis    | lacrosse   | surfing | snowboarding    |

