.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
Music-Genre: rock, punk, reggae, gospel
Color: coral, blood-red, apricot, light-blue
1. Color:blood-red != Music-Genre:rock##6
2. Color:apricot is on the right of Color:light-blue##1
3. Music-Genre:gospel is not to the left of Color:light-blue##8
4. Music-Genre:reggae == Color:coral##1
5. Music-Genre:gospel is somewhere between Color:blood-red and Color:coral##7
6. Music-Genre:gospel is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1
7. Color:apricot is between Color:light-blue and Music-Genre:reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | punk    | gospel | rock | reggae |
| Color   | blood-red | light-blue      | apricot     | coral     |

 